Ultra thick Bakery Style Chocolate Chip Cookies feature golden brown edges with ooey and gooey centers 🍪😍 Full of sweet butterscotch & chocolate flavors, this is the only chocolate chip cookie recipe you'll ever need!⁠ 😋 Can be made in 30 minutes (but are even better if you let the dough chill overnight!!) 🤤 Recipe linked in my profile @handletheheat 💕⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠

Baked strawberry lemon doughnuts

node.text:
This is my face whenever I shock someone by telling them the doughnut they're eating is BAKED not fried 😂⁠⁠
⁠⁠
These Baked Strawberry Lemon Doughnuts taste almost identical to fried doughnuts thanks to an ultra rich dough! And that vibrant thick icing? Not a drop of food color involved thanks to a secret ingredient! 🍓⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Find out what it is and peek the full recipe by tapping the link in my bio 💕⁠⁠

How to make a water bath for cheesecake

node.text:
Today is #NationalCheesecakeDay so I thought I'd share the secret to a perfectly smooth, luscious, and creamy cheesecake... 🍰⁠⁠
⁠⁠
The key to a cheesecake that bakes evenly and without cracks? A WATER BATH! 😇⁠⁠ it’s also got a way better more velvety even texture with each slice!
⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
Today I'm sharing exactly how to prepare a water bath for perfect cheesecake every time!⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
The photos of a cheesecake baked with and without a water bath are INSANE. Just swipe here to see (and more in the blog post!) 🤯⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
Tap the link in my profile + click on this photo for the full article with step-by-step photos! ⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
⁠⠀⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
